Description: Vector similarity search for trading pattern recognition
SQL Query: SELECT id, content, embedding <=> '[0.1,0.2,0.3]'::vector as distance FROM memory_system.memory_embeddings ORDER BY embedding <=> '[0.1,0.2,0.3]'::vector LIMIT 5

Description: Multi-table join for strategy performance analysis
SQL Query: SELECT t.id, t.symbol, t.side, t.quantity, s.strategy_name FROM trading_core.trades t JOIN trading_core.strategies s ON t.strategy_id = s.strategy_id WHERE t.created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '24 hours' LIMIT 10

SELECT symbol, SUM(CASE WHEN side = 'buy' THEN quantity ELSE -quantity END) as net_position, AVG(price) as avg_price FROM trading_core.trades WHERE created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '7 days' GROUP BY symbol ORDER BY ABS(SUM(CASE WHEN side = 'buy' THEN quantity ELSE -quantity END)) DESC LIMIT 5

Description: Context-aware memory retrieval for conversation continuity
SQL Query: SELECT c.id, c.user_message, c.solace_response, c.created_at FROM memory_system.conversations c WHERE c.embedding <=> '[0.5,0.6,0.7]'::vector < 0.8 ORDER BY c.created_at DESC LIMIT 3

SELECT d.id, d.decision_type, d.confidence_score, d.created_at FROM solace_core.solace_decisions d WHERE d.confidence_score > 0.7 AND d.created_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '1 hour' ORDER BY d.confidence_score DESC LIMIT 5

Query Name: Tool Registry Search - AI Agent Tools
Description: Vector search for finding relevant AI tools
SQL Query: SELECT tool_id, tool_name, description FROM tool_system.tool_registry ORDER BY embedding <=> '[0.8,0.9,0.1]'::vector LIMIT 3

SELECT 'trading' as domain, COUNT(*) as record_count FROM trading_core.trades UNION ALL SELECT 'memory' as domain, COUNT(*) as record_count FROM memory_system.memory_embeddings UNION ALL SELECT 'solace' as domain, COUNT(*) as record_count FROM solace_core.solace_decisions
